{"tha-ap142:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap142:0.2":"Sobhitavagga ","tha-ap142:0.3":"10 Piyalaphaladayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap142:1.1":"“Paravato tada asim, ","tha-ap142:1.2":"param anuparodhako; ","tha-ap142:1.3":"Pabbhare seyyam kappemi, ","tha-ap142:1.4":"avidure sikhisatthuno. ","tha-ap142:2.1":"Sayam patanca passami, ","tha-ap142:2.2":"buddham lokagganayakam; ","tha-ap142:2.3":"Deyyadhammo ca me natthi, ","tha-ap142:2.4":"dvipadindassa tadino. ","tha-ap142:3.1":"Piyalaphalamadaya, ","tha-ap142:3.2":"agamam buddhasantikam; ","tha-ap142:3.3":"Patiggahesi bhagava, ","tha-ap142:3.4":"lokajettho narasabho. ","tha-ap142:4.1":"Tato param upadaya, ","tha-ap142:4.2":"paricarim vinayakam; ","tha-ap142:4.3":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap142:4.4":"tattha kalankato aham. ","tha-ap142:5.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap142:5.2":"yam phalam adadim aham; ","tha-ap142:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap142:5.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap142:6.1":"Ito pannarase kappe, ","tha-ap142:6.2":"tayo asum piyalino; ","tha-ap142:6.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap142:6.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap142:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap142:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap142:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap142:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma piyalaphaladayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap142:9.1":"Piyalaphaladayakattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap142:10.1":"Sobhitavaggo cuddasamo. ","tha-ap142:11.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap142:12.1":"Sobhitasudassano ca, ","tha-ap142:12.2":"candano pupphachadano; ","tha-ap142:12.3":"Raho campakapupphi ca, ","tha-ap142:12.4":"atthasandassakena ca. ","tha-ap142:13.1":"Ekapasadi saladado, ","tha-ap142:13.2":"dasamo phaladayako; ","tha-ap142:13.3":"Gathayo sattati dve ca, ","tha-ap142:13.4":"ganitayo vibhavibhi. "}